    "# Modeling: MultiModal AI — Homework 3\n",
    "**MAS.S60 / 6.S985 • Spring 2026 • MIT**\n",
    "\n",
    "In this homework, you will explore Vision-Language Models (VLMs) and gain hands-on experience fine-tuning one.\n",
    "\n",
    "---\n",
    "\n",
    "## Environment Setup\n",
    "\n",
