    "```\n",
    "mmai-data/\n",
    "├── images/\n",
    "│   ├── image_01.jpg\n",
    "│   ├── image_02.jpg\n",
    "│   ├── ...\n",
    "└── data.jsonl\n",
    "```\n",
    "\n",
    "As part of this task. You should split the data into a train and test split. **The test split should consist of the images of data that you will not use in training.**\n"
